'''[[gallic]] [[acid]]'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[phenolic]] [[carboxylic acid]], 3,4,5-trihydroxybenzoic acid, found in [[gall]]s, [[tea]], the [[bark]] of some [[tree]]s etc; a constituent of [[tannin]]
#{{chemistry}} the supposed acid H<sub>3</sub>GaO<sub>3</sub>, the acid form of the [[amphoteric]] [[gallium hydroxide]] Ga(OH)<sub>3</sub>, known only as alkali metal salts

